XMLrev - a XML revision tool

Prerequisites:
 * bash
 * xmldiff
 * xsltproc
 * sp
 * libxml2-utils
 * docbook-xsl

xmlrev is a tool based on xmldiff reads two version of a document and
outputs a new document that includes the revision information
(parts added, removed and changed). This document can then
be rendered with a specific stylesheet that renders the changes.

Try:
	xmlrev doc.xml new_doc.xml > rev_doc.xml

Then render rev_doc.xml with the docbook_rev.xsl stylesheet.

